NFS.NIS2-CORE 
NFS.NIS2-SERVER 
NFS.KEY-CORE 
NFS.NFS-64SLIB 
NFS.NIS2-CLIENT 
NFS.NIS2-CORE 
NFS.NIS2-SERVER 
action: install patch PHNE_36260 or subsequent 

HP-UX B.11.31 
============== 
NFS.NIS2-SERVER 
NFS.NIS2-SERVER 
action: install patch PHNE_36449 or subsequent 

END AFFECTED VERSIONS 


RESOLUTION
HP is providing the following patches to resolve the vulnerability. 
The updates are available from: http://itrc.hp.com 

OS Release 
 Patch ID 
 
HP-UX B.11.11
 PHNE_36168 or subsequent
 
HP-UX B.11.23
 PHNE_36260 or subsequent
 
HP-UX B.11.31
 PHNE_36449 or subsequent
 

MANUAL ACTIONS: No 

PRODUCT SPECIFIC INFORMATION 

HP-UX Software Assistant: 
HP-UX Software Assistant is an enhanced application that replaces HP-UX Security Patch Check. It analyzes all HP-issued Security Bulletins and lists recommended actions that may apply to a specific HP-UX system. It can also download patches and create a depot automatically. For more information see: https://www.hp.com/go/swa 

HISTORY: Version 1 (rev.1) - 19 December 2007 Initial Release 

